HEADWORD: Insupportable
<hw>In`sup*port"a*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>insupportabilis</ets>: cf. F. <ets>insupportable</ets>. See
<er>In-</er> not, and <er>Support</er>.]</ety> <def>Incapable of being
supported or borne; unendurable; insufferable; intolerable; <as>as,
<ex>insupportable</ex> burdens; <ex>insupportable</ex> pain.</as></def>
-- <wordforms><wf>In`sup*port"a*ble*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos> --
<wf>In`sup*port"a*bly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

